## Notes

- The existing schema.sql indicates this database is from "Shiori" bookmark manager - ensure compatibility
- Account table exists but authentication is out of scope for MVP
- Consider future enhancement: content fetching (has_content flag suggests this was planned)
- Tag management should be case-insensitive to avoid duplicates ("Go" vs "go")
- The schema supports fulltext search on title, excerpt, and content - leverage this for performance
